Package org.amcp.core

Class Event

java.lang.Object
org.amcp.core.Event
public final class Event extends Object
Represents an event in the AMCP mesh. Events are the primary means of communication between agents. They contain a topic, payload, and metadata for routing and processing.
Since:
1.0.0
Version:
1.5.0
Author:
AMCP Development Team
